The paper proposes a new method for learning variational autoencoders (VAEs) that demonstrates excellent performance across multiple unsupervised and semi-supervised problems, including semi-supervised analysis of the ImageNet data. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
